cova.data

Class Abstraction

  • java.lang.Object
    • cova.data.Abstraction

  • public class Abstraction
extends Object
    The Class Abstraction contains the constraint of current statement and a set of taints.

      • shallowMeet

        public static Abstraction shallowMeet(Abstraction a,
                                      Abstraction b)
        Meet operation of two given abstractions shallowly. The constraints are merged with disjunction and the taints are simply merged with set union.
        Parameters:
        a - the first abstraction
        b - the second abstraction
        Returns:
        the abstraction of a and b after performing the shallow meet operation.
